# Ferris wheel (ferris_wheel flat ride): the rotating wheel only.
# Disc in the X-Y plane, axle along Z, centred at the origin (the spin
# lifts it to the axle). The A-frame legs are base-game graphics, so the
# object provides only the wheel; gondola.obj orbits as a second mesh.
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
mtllib materials.mtl

